text: Colette, also released under the name of Prisoner of Auschwitz, is a 2013 Slovakian Czech Dutch World War II biographical drama movie directed by Milan Cieslar and starring Andrej Hryc, Eric Bouwer, Jirí Mádl, Jan Cina, Zuzana Mauréry. ==Other websites== * Category:2013 drama movies Category:2010s war movies Category:2010s biographical movies Category:Slovakian movies Category:Czech biographical movies Category:Czech drama movies Category:Dutch biographical movies Category:Dutch drama movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Milan Cieslar
title: Colette (2013 movie)
